  "title": "6616 - Store Packer / Store Assistant (5.5 days alt Sat)",
  "description": "<p>Working Hours: 5.5 days a week (8:30 AM to 5:30 PM)\nwith alternate Saturdays from 8:30 AM to 12:30 PM </p><p>Experience: Relevant experience preferred </p><p>Working location: Jurong East<br /><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ol><li>Pick items from warehouse shelves according to order   specifications </li><li>Prepare items for shipment by checking quality, securely wrapping, and boxing products </li><li>Checking their quality, securely wrapping and boxing them </li><li>Receive, store, pack, and unpack goods </li><li>Deliver goods from suppliers when required </li><li>Load and unload vehicles/trucks </li><li>Carry and move goods as part of daily operation </li><li>Assist with stock counts when required </li><li>Maintain regular housekeeping standards in the warehouse </li><li>Work closely with the warehouse team to meet daily fulfillment targets </li><li>Perform any other lawful and reasonable duties as assigned </li></ol><p><br />We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified</p><p>Whatsapp: +6591357134</p><p>Juanna Ng Hui Kee Reg no: R1766616</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA number: 14C7279</p><p><br /></p>",
